If you want to make it reusable, declare a real class with fields:

    class WorkoutTimerTask extends TimerTask {  

        int secondsWorkout;
        int cache;

        WorkoutTimerTask(int secondsWorkout, int cache) {
            this.secondsWorkout = secondsWorkout;
